oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Narvel Felts interview - Joe Suglia - WBUK - part 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Part two of a recording of an interview with Narvel Felts (performer), conducted by Joe Suglia for radio station WBUK.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Joe Suglia introduces Narvel Felts -- Felts talks about Lonely Teardrops -- Felts talks about the origin of his full name -- Felts talks about his method of travel while touring -- Felts talks about his band members -- Felts talks about his latest single, My Prayer -- Felts promotes Joe Suglia and WBUK
